      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.413668,
      "replayEndSec": 10.922135,
      "narrationText": "El primer push a otra máquina transfiere la imagen completa, y la salida lo dice claramente: dos gigabytes transferidos, marcado como full. Esta es la línea base.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-01.39d55053.mp3",
      "textHash": "39d55053c478514464812dd3e6b8af7e917885df440debcc3faebecad0582107",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.524082,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-01-after.5192b68d.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 11.964082,
      "afterTextHash": "5192b68dffd3e6c520eb338780868949a18af3b39bc10f245e0777150d34144e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-delta-transfer-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 10.922135,
      "replayEndSec": 21.404869,
      "narrationText": "Cambia un poco de datos: cincuenta megabytes de dos gigabytes.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-02.22659582.mp3",
      "textHash": "22659582d3676c496d54469304367fd1de76557726ecbe48fa88cb17e713808e",
      "audioDurationSec": 4.754286,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-02-after.87bfa710.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.507755,
      "afterTextHash": "87bfa71050681eb20f858f4afaf618df3ebe6e80648316a05642a28f56fbe367"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-delta-transfer-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 21.404869,
      "replayEndSec": 29.764702,
      "narrationText": "Haz push de nuevo. El mismo comando, pero esta vez fíjate en la salida: unos cincuenta megabytes transferidos, marcado como delta, sobre una imagen de dos gigabytes. Solo viajaron los bloques modificados.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-03.a5bdcdb4.mp3",
      "textHash": "a5bdcdb413a6419f9cab64b979e6d72a04cd38728178664ee900f6ca7c1e743d",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.680816,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-03-after.2e413b74.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 7.810612,
      "afterTextHash": "2e413b748d40acda3e63a882617603c512c991c53e0c6d43e017bf1774ae56ec"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-delta-transfer-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 29.764702,
      "replayEndSec": 34.159829,
      "narrationText": "Ambas máquinas tienen el mismo repository, actualizado en segundos. Ejecútalo cada hora si quieres, el coste es el cambio, no el tamaño.",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-04.944b1f5f.mp3",
      "textHash": "944b1f5f4d3bfabcb2b83076941c9a10d69ba460623b1f7c016b8bab0233f4ae",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.717551,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/es/tutorial-delta-transfer/tutorial-delta-transfer-04-after.db781bb1.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.866122,
      "afterTextHash": "db781bb182f154cee03070bb6da25d3f93ad180ec176b929130a63772d95fb7e"
    }
